title: Redfish Power Redundancy
agents: agent_redfish
catalog: hw/server/redfish
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the power supply redundancy state of Redfish compatible devices.
 It reports the redundancy mode, minimum needed and maximum supported power supplies,
 and the current number of power supplies in the redundancy set.

discovery:
 One service is created for each redundancy entry.

item:
 The member ID of the redundancy entry.
